## ⚡ Context Gathering is Mandatory (Tiered)

**Time Investment:** 0-35 minutes (proportional to task complexity) 
**Time Saved:** 50-90% (hours to days) 
**Proven ROI:** Multiple 99% time savings in actual implementations

**Context depth is PROPORTIONAL to task complexity:**
- Quick fixes: 0-2 min (just find the code)
- Targeted tasks: 5-10 min (plan section + rationale)
- New phases: 15-20 min (rationale + connections + plan)
- Architectural: 25-35 min (full rationale system + philosophy)

**DO NOT skip context gathering to "save time" - it costs more later.**
**DO NOT over-prepare for small tasks -- that wastes time too.**

