## ✅ Before Starting ANY Implementation

**Follow the tiered checklist from `docs/plans/methodology/SESSION_START_CHECKLIST.md`.**

**Minimum requirements for ALL tiers (MANDATORY):**
- [ ] I have classified the task tier (Quick / Targeted / Phase / Architectural)
- [ ] I have followed the checklist for my tier
- [ ] I have searched for existing implementations
- [ ] I understand where new code should be placed

**Additional for Targeted tier and above:**
- [ ] I have read the relevant phase rationale (`docs/plans/rationale/PHASE_X_RATIONALE.md`)
- [ ] I have checked the pre-flight checklist in the rationale

**Additional for Phase tier and above:**
- [ ] I have read the Foundational Decisions that apply
- [ ] I have read the Cross-Phase Connections for affected phases
- [ ] I have created a TODO list
- [ ] I have communicated my plan to the user
- [ ] User has approved the approach

**Additional for Architectural tier:**
- [ ] I have answered the four doors questions
- [ ] I have identified all cross-cutting contracts affected
- [ ] I have analyzed the chain reaction of my changes

**If ANY required checkbox for your tier is unchecked, DO NOT START CODING.**

