## 📊 Success Metrics (Proven)

Following this protocol:
- Phase 1 Integration: 15-20 min context → Saved 5 days (99%)
- Targeted task in known phase: 5-10 min → Saved hours of wrong-direction work
- Architectural cross-phase work: 25-35 min → Saved days of rework

**NOT following this protocol:**
- Risk duplicating existing work
- Risk wrong architecture/placement
- Risk breaking cross-cutting contracts
- 2-10x longer implementation time

---

## 🎯 The Golden Rule

```
Context depth proportional to task complexity.
Quick tasks get quick context.
Big tasks get thorough context.
NEVER skip context. NEVER over-prepare.
Match the investment to the task.
```

